'''拉拉·古特-贝赫拉米'''（{{lang-it|Lara Gut-Behrami}}，{{bd|1991年|4月27日||}}），娘家姓'''古特'''（{{lang|it|Gut}}），生于提契诺州索伦戈，是一名瑞士女子高山滑雪运动员。拉拉的父亲Pauli是一名前高山滑雪选手<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pyeongchang2018.com/en/game-time/results/OWG2018/en/alpine-skiing/athlete-profile-n3034551-lara-gut.htm|title=Athlete Profile: Lara GUT|work=Pyeongchang 2018|accessdate=2021-03-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180420020349/https://www.pyeongchang2018.com/en/game-time/results/OWG2018/en/alpine-skiing/athlete-profile-n3034551-lara-gut.htm|archivedate=2018-04-20}}</ref>，弟弟Ian同样从事高山滑雪，但代表[[列支敦士登|列支敦士登]]参加比赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.olympicchannel.com/en/stories/features/detail/top-five-facts-lara-gut-behrami-skiing/|title=Top five things to know about Lara Gut-Behrami|publisher=[[奥林匹克频道|Olympic Channel]]|date=2021-02-08|accessdate=2021-03-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208140129/https://www.olympicchannel.com/en/stories/features/detail/top-five-facts-lara-gut-behrami-skiing/|archivedate=2021-02-08}}</ref>。拉拉于2016年获得年度最佳瑞士女运动员奖<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.schweizer-illustrierte.ch/stars/schweiz/sports-awards-sportler-des-jahres-fabian-cancellara-lara-gut|script-title=de:Gut und Cancellara sind Sportler des Jahres!|publisher={{lang|de|Schweizer Illustrierte}}|date=2016-12-18|accessdate=2021-03-06|archiveurl=https://archive.is/JQgh6|archivedate=2021-03-06}}</ref>，2018年7月与足球选手[[瓦隆·贝赫拉米|瓦隆·贝赫拉米]]结婚<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.tele1.ch/artikel/151733/lara-gut-und-valon-behrami-haben-geheiratet | script-title=de:Lara Gut und Valon Behrami haben geheiratet |work =tele1.ch |date=2018-07-12|accessdate=2018-07-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712152839/https://www.tele1.ch/artikel/151733/lara-gut-und-valon-behrami-haben-geheiratet|archivedate=2018-07-12}}</ref>，之后她开始使用[[双姓|双姓]]“古特-贝赫拉米”参加比赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://apnews.com/article/f487c780eaeb465e842440ca9e683ba5|title=After recent wedding, Swiss skier is now Lara Gut-Behrami|publisher=[[美联社|Associated Press]]|date=2018-11-26|accessdate=2021-03-06|archiveurl=https://archive.is/5Onyz|archivedate=2021-03-06}}</ref>。

